bcea_cases_studyid.description:
This table adds the information from BCEA cases, BCEA Ei_pending, NFA, Deaths_b, Aboriginal Status,  and BCEA_OOP 
to BCEA involvement.  It creates a unique record for each person-month.

Because a very small number of people are involved with more than one case in a month, there is ambiguity in which 
characteristic is the relevant one.  This program picks the larger value (ie. the selection is arbitrary).  
Some of the people in BCEA involvement do not have an associated case, so some of the information is null. 
Corrected birth dates have been added. family type and age of youngest child have been fixed.
